The paper focuses on scene recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves building a layout graph network and incorporating topological structures, which suggests the use of machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and graph theory (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of datasets such as MIT67 and SUN397, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
